name: Organic Heirloom Tomatoes
description: Vine-ripened heirloom tomatoes in various colors including red, yellow, and purple. Perfect for salads, sandwiches, or cooking. Grown without pesticides or synthetic fertilizers.

name: Fresh Spinach Bunches
description: Tender, fresh spinach leaves perfect for salads, smoothies, or cooking. Harvested this morning and packed with nutrients. Grown using organic methods.

name: Artisan Goat Cheese
description: Creamy, handcrafted goat cheese made from milk from our grass-fed goats. Aged for 30 days for the perfect tangy flavor. Great for cheese boards or cooking.

name: Fresh Whole Milk
description: Creamy, fresh whole milk from our grass-fed Holstein cows. Pasteurized but not homogenized for the best flavor and nutrition. Available in glass bottles.

name: Aged Cheddar Cheese
description: Sharp, aged cheddar cheese aged for 12 months. Rich, complex flavor perfect for cheese boards, cooking, or snacking. Made from our farm's fresh milk.

name: Greek Yogurt
description: Thick, creamy Greek yogurt made from our fresh milk. High in protein and probiotics. Perfect for breakfast, smoothies, or as a healthy snack.

name: Honeycrisp Apples
description: Crisp, sweet Honeycrisp apples perfect for eating fresh or baking. Known for their exceptional crunch and balanced sweet-tart flavor.

name: Northern Spy Apples
description: Classic heirloom variety perfect for baking pies and making cider. Tart flavor that develops sweetness when cooked. A traditional favorite.

name: Fresh Apple Cider
description: Fresh-pressed apple cider made from a blend of our best apples. Unpasteurized and unfiltered for maximum flavor. Perfect for fall drinking.

name: Fresh Strawberries
description: Sweet, juicy strawberries picked at peak ripeness. Perfect for eating fresh, making jam, or adding to desserts. Grown using organic methods.

name: Blueberries
description: Plump, sweet blueberries bursting with flavor. High in antioxidants and perfect for smoothies, baking, or eating fresh. U-pick available on weekends.

name: Raspberries
description: Tart, sweet raspberries perfect for jams, desserts, or eating fresh. Delicate fruit that's hand-picked daily for maximum freshness.

name: Whole Wheat Flour
description: Freshly milled whole wheat flour from our own wheat. Stone-ground for maximum nutrition and flavor. Perfect for bread baking and cooking.

name: Rolled Oats
description: Old-fashioned rolled oats perfect for oatmeal, granola, or baking. Grown and processed on our farm for maximum freshness and nutrition.

name: Barley
description: Pearl barley perfect for soups, stews, and pilafs. Nutty flavor and chewy texture. Great source of fiber and nutrients.

name: Cherry Tomatoes
description: Sweet, bite-sized cherry tomatoes perfect for snacking, salads, or roasting. Grown year-round in our climate-controlled greenhouse.

name: Bell Peppers
description: Colorful bell peppers in red, yellow, and green. Sweet and crisp, perfect for cooking or eating raw. Grown using hydroponic methods.

name: Fresh Basil
description: Aromatic fresh basil perfect for pesto, Italian cooking, or garnishing. Grown in our greenhouse for consistent quality year-round.

name: Microgreens Mix
description: Nutrient-dense microgreens mix including arugula, radish, and broccoli sprouts. Perfect for salads, sandwiches, or as a garnish. Packed with vitamins and minerals.
